                            <comment id="12904467" author="olgan" created="Tue, 31 Aug 2010 01:52:31 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I made one additional change and renamed SPLIT into STRSPLIT to avoid conflict with SPLIT operator&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
